blockChainEnhanceDesc: Blockchain for business uses a shared and immutable ledger that can only be accessed by members with permission. Network members control what information each organization or member may see, and what actions each can take. Blockchain is sometimes called a trustless network not because business partners don’t trust each other, but because they don’t have to.
